Long definition: Alphanumeric ID number for stock management unit (SMU) demographic unit. An official list of SMU ID's and corresponding names can be found in the NuSEDS CU/SMU Crosswalk
Coded Wire Tag for the indicator population (used as a representative population for the SMU).
Auto-generated unique identifier for the record.
Total number of spawners (fish that returned to spawn) for the year.
Total Recruits (number of new fish added to the population via spawning, by brood year).
